                  <decoDesc>

                     <decoNote type="other" xml:id="d2"/>
                     <decoNote type="mixed" xml:id="d3">
                        <p>Three crude polychrome pictures (black, pink and brown): </p>
                        <p>
                           <locus target="#1"/>) An angel with a sword, at the top of the scroll</p>
                        <p>
                           <locus target="#2"/>) A face framed with eight “horns” (“The Net of Solomon”), in the midst of Text II </p>
                        <p>
                           <locus target="#3"/>) A panel made of squares and faces, with a cross in the middle, before Text V.</p>
                        
                     </decoNote>
                  </decoDesc>
                  <additions>
                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="a1">
                           <p>በስመ፡አብ፡"… ፡[“magic letters”] ጸሎት፡በእንተ፡ባርያ፡ወሌጌዎን፡ወዛር፡ውላጅ፡ዘበንያ፡ወሸግያ፡በርደሌ፡ወጉዳሌ፡ፌራ፡ወንዳድ፡...</p>
                           
                        </item>
                     </list>
                  </additions>
